    "description": "<u><strong>ONLINE PARTY MULTIPLAYER</strong></u><br>Challenge your friends from anywhere is the world in this ever changing gameplay party game up to 4 players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/6f86b468053f5d083f4956345ba92ca3.poster.avif?t=1741983507\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/6f86b468053f5d083f4956345ba92ca3.webm?t=1741983507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/6f86b468053f5d083f4956345ba92ca3.mp4?t=1741983507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR LOADOUT</strong></u><br>New round, new me! Swap your current set of abilities every time a new round starts. Discover all the available  combinations and counter your friends playstyle at any time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/89d0b0a986f7975a7f9bca2728908747.poster.avif?t=1741983507\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/89d0b0a986f7975a7f9bca2728908747.webm?t=1741983507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/89d0b0a986f7975a7f9bca2728908747.mp4?t=1741983507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>CHANGING GAMEPLAY</strong></u><br>Every round offers a different way of defeating your friends as well as a new set of rules for this. Play all vs all, play by teams, win by killing your opponents or maybe just push them out of the arena.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/e196c7e2e62bde9364b8c1a982d96b77.poster.avif?t=1741983507\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/e196c7e2e62bde9364b8c1a982d96b77.webm?t=1741983507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012280/extras/e196c7e2e62bde9364b8c1a982d96b77.mp4?t=1741983507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>FAST GAMES</strong></u><br>If you and your friends have just a little bit of time for playing, this might be perfect for you! Every game lasts between 8 to 15 minutes, win 10 rounds and you all will be free to go (or maybe play again)",
